      <title>韩国因非法裸卖空对全球银行处以创纪录的 2000 万美元罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/korea-fines-global-banks-record-20-million-for-illegal-naked-short-selling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国决定对两家全球投资银行和其中一家公司的当地分支机构处以裸卖空总额 265 亿韩元（2030 万美元）的罚款，这是该国有史以来对这种非法行为的最大处罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/korea-fines-global-banks-record-20-million-for-illegal-naked-short-selling</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储和日本央行路径可能逆转，资产管理公司转而看涨日元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/asset-managers-turn-bullish-on-yen-as-fed-boj-path-may-reverse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于越来越多的人认为日本央行可能会在 2024 年结束超宽松政策，同时主要央行降息，资产管理公司自 5 月份以来首次从看跌日元转为看涨日元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/asset-managers-turn-bullish-on-yen-as-fed-boj-path-may-reverse</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 02:06:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>央行通过固定汇率提供人民币支持令企业头疼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/pboc-s-yuan-support-through-fixing-causes-headache-for-companies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年，中国央行利用人为强势的参考汇率来捍卫弱势货币。这种干预给一些人带来了意想不到的痛苦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/pboc-s-yuan-support-through-fixing-causes-headache-for-companies</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于反对派拒绝投票，刚果公布了更多民意调查结果</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-24/congo-publishes-more-poll-results-as-opposition-rejects-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国选举委员会公布了上周选举的另一份抽样结果，称现任总统菲利克斯·齐塞克迪遥遥领先，反对派候选人因涉嫌欺诈而呼吁取消投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-24/congo-publishes-more-poll-results-as-opposition-rejects-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 21:16:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
